  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "NBKRIST gave me confidence, skills, and the right environment to grow into a future engineer.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "Supportive environment with good faculty and infrastructure. Great opportunities for learning and activities.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "The peaceful campus and supportive faculty make learning enjoyable every day.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "Every semester brought new learning opportunities and confidence.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "NBKRIST gave me confidence and direction.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "My college years were instrumental in shaping my professional path. The faculty's guidance combined with exposure to industry-oriented projects and cultural activities, helped me build a well-rounded skill set.This holistic development has been key to my growth in the software industry..",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "I am proud to be part of NBKRIST.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "NBKRIST laid the foundation for my successful software career.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "My journey from classroom to corporate began at NBKRIST.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "I owe much of my professional success to NBKRIST.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "content": "We saw remarkable growth in our child after joining NBKRIST.",
    "source": "https://nbkrist.org/"
  },
